name: Equilibrium
description:
Shot on Canon EOS 5/Fujifilm Industrial 400 | 1/30 Speed | C41 Process | Noritsu Scan | 2856 × 1893px

Shoot this moment when attending indonesian track cycling team training camp for Asian Games 2018, it's very challanging for me to shoot this fast train because inside this velodrome i doesn't get enough natural light and i just brought my Fujifilm Industrial Film with 400 Iso. All i can do is just take a deep breath, wait,

and shoot.
